{"tid":105673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國北京民族樂團赴美國演出 傳被集體拒簽","createTime":"2017-02-03T05:27:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T15:24:19.000Z","uid":35790,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"25fd658bebe83241e1f6e100a6e6499c199388c4","tid":105673,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T05:27:01.000Z","msg":"中共演出團赴美 被集體拒簽 <br />\n<br />\n【新唐人亞太台 2017 年 02 月 03 日訊】<br />\n<br />\n美國總統川普上臺後，對入境美國的相關政策 嚴格把關。近日傳出北京民族樂團原定在2月7日赴洛杉磯演出，然而，這批由37人組成的 演出團體被集體拒簽。據負責本次活動的僑團代表透露，美使館拒簽的理由有二個，一是 原定的公益演出被發現「賣票」；二是原定演出只有西雅圖一場，後來又增加洛杉磯、舊 金山等城市，簽證官認為前後說法不一，所以拒簽。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/sfUQnO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FsfUQnO&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=7d206af4\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/sfUQnO</a>"},{"pid":"f48c5a539aefd8d7558cebc6d836315cc38c4c86","tid":105673,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T05:27:27.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"316ea7bce95eafff4121941a69adb53d2d05d6e8","tid":105673,"uid":62391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T05:32:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6cc91b01a6c9ff9e347ce2415c625a82589040c7","tid":105673,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T11:50:38.000Z","msg":"中國人有句說話，叫能不回來的，就不回來了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9acdb0b9657fdd5b0cba3064c26dce849f7a8947","tid":105673,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T11:54:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中共演出團赴美 被集體拒簽 <br />\n<br />\n【新唐人亞太台 2017 年 02 月 03 日訊】<br />\n<br />\n美國總統川普上臺後，對入境美國的相關政策 嚴格把關。近日傳出北京民族樂團原定在2月7日赴洛杉磯演出，然而，這批由37人組成的 演出團體被集體拒簽。據負責本次活動的僑團代表透露，美使館拒簽的理由有二個，一是 原定的公益演出被發現「賣票」；二是<span style=\"color: red;\">原定演出只有西雅圖一場，後來又增加洛杉磯、舊 金山等城市，簽證官認為前後說法不一，所以拒簽。 <br />\n[url]https</span>://<a href=\"http://goo.gl/sfUQnO[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FsfUQnO%5B%2Furl%5D&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=7b4f9d11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">goo.gl/sfUQnO[/url]</a></blockquote><br />\n呢個理由聽落好似幾合理，不過唔熟美國法律，唔知係咪一向都會reject"},{"pid":"cf4e9efca89fdab35e988828a5481d31299ed158","tid":105673,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T12:31:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"304d1f29b0d7d78beacd6b84002dd2450ce70b5b","tid":105673,"uid":35410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T13:23:39.000Z","msg":"佢老母有閪人睇咩，咪又喺做比啲所謂愛支國嘅人睇，拒絕入境做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b845a8755e2fd66a318a82e6a370273b3b88235b","tid":105673,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T14:07:34.000Z","msg":"同北擊D人一樣"},{"pid":"b6ddfd066b0a3b778d4858b34be2244b16078123","tid":105673,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T15:24:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}